Tiny Stray Dog Does Not Know What To Think When Rescuers Sneak Up On Him Subscribe to Reshareworthy! It's FREE and always will be! 
Hope For Paws was called about a tiny dog living between the L.A. River and the railroad tracks. When they arrived, they realized the dog was in a precarious spot and needed to be approached cautiously. But none of them were expecting Diesel to react as he did…
